data.description: Welcome to 214 Ash St, a charming 3 bed 1 bath ranch nestled on a desirable corner lot in Cambridge. With its open floor plan the options are endless.  This delightful home offers convenience, comfort, and a prime location. Enjoy the ease of being just moments away from shopping and restaurants. Families will appreciate the proximity to schools, making it easy for children to walk or bike to class. Brand new Roof in 2021.
